    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the pros and cons, but some people say that because of how fast things are getting worse with the climate, we don't really have a choice but to go nuclear. do you think that's a fair assessment or is that just being alarmist?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
