      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The urgency of the climate crisis absolutely necessitates a rapid pivot to reliable, zero-emission energy sources, making nuclear power a pragmatic necessity for many. While some frame this as alarmism, the scientific consensus on accelerating climate impacts demands we utilize every available low-carbon tool. Therefore, viewing nuclear power as a critical, non-negotiable component of climate mitigation is a rational response to the current environmental emergency.",
